   "EXECUTE requires net EV >= 5bp AND P >= 1.15x the base rate AND >=30 historical occurrences",
   "Suggested size = quarter-Kelly on the two-outcome bet, capped at 5% of book \u2014 a research hint, never advice",
   "Decay guard: once forward evidence (>=30 samples over >=10 distinct days) runs below 90% of the backtest estimate, EXECUTE demotes to WAIT",
